  "notes": "Born Jul 18, 1697 in Kingston, Ulster County, NY. Son of Mattheus DuBois (1679-1748) and Sara Matthysen (1678-1748). Many siblings born in Kingston: Mattheus (1698), Hiskia (1701), Ephraim (1703), Johannes (1706), Tjaatje (1707), Jesse (1709), Catrina (1715), Gideon (1719-1815), Peter (1720). Son: Elias (Elijah) DuBois (1713-1786). Father Mattheus died Jun 2, 1748 in Poughkeepsie. Mother Sara died 1748. Died 1751 in Ulster County at age 54."
